-- Carige foundation shareholder to subcribe pro rata to rights issue
-- 
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 09:48AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 26 (Reuters) - The main foundation shareholder of Banca Carige <CRGI.MI> said on Thursday it would subscribe its share of the lender's rights issue over the next few days.

The foundation holds 19 percent of Carige which has launched a cash call worth 800 million euros ($1.1 billion).